The final answer must start from `2`.

---

# Connect Previous Group to Current Group

```java
if (ktail != null) {
    ktail.next = revHead;
}
```

This connects the previous reversed group to the current reversed group.

Example:

After reversing first group:

```text
2 -> 1
     ^
   ktail
```

After reversing second group:

```text
4 -> 3
```

Now:

```java
