## Helper Function Code

```java
private ListNode reverseLinkedList(ListNode head, int k) {
    
    ListNode newHead = null;
    ListNode ptr = head;
    
    while (k > 0) {
        ListNode nextNode = ptr.next;
        ptr.next = newHead;
        newHead = ptr;
        ptr = nextNode;
        k--;
    }
    
    return newHead;
}
```

